description: Dewmar International BMC, Inc. operates as a brand management services company in the United States and internationally. The company specializes in developing or acquiring new products, brands, or companies for launch or distribution in various markets. It manages multiple brands and services, including consumer good categories, and health and wellness industry verticals, as well as offers outsourced sales and marketing services. The company also provides yella, purp, and easta pink flavored relaxation beverage products under the brand name of Lean Slow Motion Potion. Dewmar International BMC, Inc. is headquartered in Clinton, Mississippi.
